
<div class="contextual-help-item principal-help"  i18n:domain="novaideo">
    <p i18n:translate="">
        Before they are published, ideas are subject to moderation.
    </p>
    <p i18n:translate="">
        As a moderator, you can either publish them, or archive them.
    </p>
    <p i18n:translate="">
        As soon as an idea is published, it will be made public, and won't be modifiable any more.
    </p>
    <p i18n:translate="">
        If it is archived, the author of the idea will need to re-work on it before s/he submits it again for publication. In this second case, you will need to explain your decision.
    </p>
</div>
